OL,7,FWhen I ask his name, he gives two
OL,8,Fanswers.
OL,10,F"My real name is Mohammad Afif
OL,11,FNaifeh," he says. Then he pauses and
OL,12,Fquietly adds, "But I'm known as The
OL,13,FGravedigger."
OL,15,FFor years, his identity was hidden.
OL,16,FHis face never seen, his voice never
OL,17,Fheard. Yet he became a pivotal figure
OL,18,Fin the pursuit of justice`an anonymous
OL,19,Fwitness to some of the darkest crimes
OL,20,Fof the 21st century.
