OL,7,FHis appearance is unremarkable: deep-
OL,8,Fset eyes, long, slicked-back hair.
OL,9,FNothing that would draw a second
OL,10,Fglance on the street.
OL,12,FYet this man has stood before
OL,13,Fparliaments around the world`including
OL,14,Fthe US Congress`and testified in
OL,15,Fcourtrooms in Germany.
OL,17,FHe reaches into his pocket and
OL,18,Fproduces a nylon mask. The moment he
OL,19,Fputs it on, the transformation is
OL,20,Fimmediate.
