OL,7,FThis is the face many people across
OL,8,Fthe world came to recognise: the
OL,9,Fmasked witness who helped bring
OL,10,Fmembers of the Syrian regime to
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,FThe man who exposed its industrial
OL,14,Fscale killing machine. 'The
OL,15,FGravedigger'.
OL,17,F"The worst moment came when the
OL,18,Ftruck's back door opened and the
OL,19,Fcorpses began spilling out," he says,
OL,20,Fas he begins to recall his life
OL,21,Fworking at the mass burial sites.
