OL,7,FRefrigerated lorries`sixteen metres
OL,8,Flong`arrived at remote burial sites
OL,9,Fwhere he had been ordered to work.
OL,11,FFor seven years, his role was simple
OL,12,Fand horrifying: bury the dead. Erase
OL,13,Fthe evidence.
OL,15,F"I was in complete shock. I didn't
OL,16,Fknow how to process what I was seeing.
OL,18,F"At first, it was just one or two
OL,19,Fvans`I assumed the bodies were
OL,20,Fsoldiers or accident victims.
