OL,7,F"I had no idea those men giving me
OL,8,Forders were from the security
OL,9,Fservices."
OL,11,FHe was not a soldier. Not a
OL,12,Fpolitician. He was a low-ranking
OL,13,Fadministrator, handed a shovel and a
OL,14,Fset of orders he could not refuse,
OL,15,Fwho, over time, would bury
OL,16,Fhundreds`perhaps thousands`of victims
OL,17,Fof the Assad regime.
