OL,7,FThat day, he buried 35 to 40
OL,8,Fbodies`some five to a grave.
OL,10,F"They were wrapped in plastic bags,
OL,11,Fstained with blood. I didn't question
OL,12,Fanything."
OL,14,FAfterwards, the men told him he was
OL,15,Fdismissed and could return to the
OL,16,Foffice. But two days later, he was
OL,17,Fordered back. And again.
