OL,7,FSoon, the vans were replaced by
OL,8,Frefrigerated lorries. The office
OL,9,Fworker who once fainted at the sight
OL,10,Fof blood had been forced into the
OL,11,Fmachinery of mass disposal.
OL,13,FAmong the dead, he began to recognise
OL,14,Fvictims.
OL,16,F"I found them among the corpses," he
OL,17,Fsays. "Some were friends from
OL,18,Fchildhood.
