OL,7,F"Their families had told me they'd
OL,8,Fgone missing in the security branches.
OL,9,FI was shocked to find them there."
OL,11,FHe lowers his voice. "Their families
OL,12,Fhad done everything`paid ransoms,
OL,13,Fbegged for answers`just to know where
OL,14,Ftheir loved ones were.
OL,16,F"We grew up in the same neighbourhood.
OL,17,FIt wasn't just one friend. There were
OL,18,Fmany."
