OL,7,FEventually, he fled Syria. After seven
OL,8,Fyears of digging graves, he escaped
OL,9,Fand was reunited with his wife and
OL,10,Fchildren`far from the sites he had
OL,11,Fbeen forced to serve.
OL,13,FAfter years as part of the regime's
OL,14,Finfrastructure, he decided to play a
OL,15,Fbigger role in the effort to bring it
OL,16,Fto justice, alongside campaigners from
OL,17,Fthe US-based Syrian Emergency Task
OL,18,FForce.
