OL,7,FMohammad spoke out. He made rare
OL,8,Fpublic appearances where he was said
OL,9,Fto be living "somewhere in Europe" or
OL,10,F"at an undisclosed location".
OL,12,FNow, the truth can be told: he made
OL,13,Fhis way to Germany after leaving
OL,14,FSyria, using one of the smuggling
OL,15,Fnetworks known to many of his
OL,16,Fcompatriots.
OL,18,FWhenever he appeared before the
OL,19,Fcameras, he wore the mask. He spoke
OL,20,Fonly in hushed tones through an
OL,21,Finterpreter.
