OL,7,FIt can now be revealed that he was one
OL,8,Fof several eyewitnesses who helped ITV
OL,9,FNews to identify a mass burial site
OL,10,Fused to dispose of Assad's opponents.
OL,12,FIn 2023, he helped us to pinpoint the
OL,13,Flocation using satellite images. Now,
OL,14,Ffour months after the collapse of the
OL,15,FAssad regime, he has revealed his
OL,16,Fidentity.
OL,18,FHe still carries the mask with him. He
OL,19,Fknows the risks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
