OL,7,F"I've abandoned my mask," he says.
OL,8,F"And now I'm afraid. Assad's people,
OL,9,For their allies`Iran, Hezbollah`they
OL,10,Fcould come for me. Even here in
OL,11,FEurope, I don't feel safe. My family
OL,12,Fdoesn't feel safe."
OL,14,FIran has been linked to assassination
OL,15,Fplots on political dissidents in
OL,16,FEurope, including in Germany.
OL,18,FMohammad knows the risks but believes
OL,19,Fhe can no longer hide.
